  "text": "Ϫ/Ϫ gastrocnemius, white and brown adipose tissues, and liver, but as expected with deletion of both AS160 and Tbc1d1, insulin-induced phospho-Akt substrates of 160 kDa were missing (Fig. 4D) . We also did not previously observe any abnormalities in insulin-elicited Akt phosphorylation in AS160 Ϫ/Ϫ mice [CITATION_1] . To test for defects in insulin secretion, we measured insulin levels after a glucose challenge in AS160",
